============================================
XSSer - Cross Site Scripter - "The Mosquito"
============================================

Cross Site "Scripter" is an automatic -framework- to detect, exploit and report XSS vulnerabilities in web-based aplications.

===================
How-to INSTALL:
===================

XSSer runs on many platforms.  It requires Python and the following libraries:

    - python-pycurl - Python bindings to libcurl
    - python-beautifulsoup - error-tolerant HTML parser for Python
    - python-geoip - Python bindings for the GeoIP IP-to-country resolver library

=========

On Debian-based systems (ex: Ubuntu), run: 

    sudo apt-get install python-pycurl python-beautifulsoup python-xml python-geoip

=========

Please report any problems you encounter using/installing XSSer to the xsser-users mailing-list:

    - mailto:xsser-users@lists.sourceforge.net

